<Base title="SocialProof for Event Venues — Testimonials That Book More Events | SocialProof" description="Event venues: collect and display client testimonials from weddings, corporate events, and celebrations to drive bookings and command premium rates.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Event Venues
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Couples and event planners evaluating venues are making one of the most significant purchasing decisions of their lives. They research obsessively. Your venue's testimonials — describing the magic of the space, the responsiveness of your team, and how the event actually felt — are the most persuasive sales tool you have.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Close more site visits and inquiries</h2>
      <p>Most couples tour 3–5 venues before booking. Many of those decisions are shaped before the tour — by what they read on your website. A curated collection of testimonials from past events, covering the venue's beauty, the team's support, and the memorable guest experience, converts browsing couples into scheduled tours.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What clients say that wins new business</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Wedding:</strong> "Our wedding was more beautiful than we imagined. The venue team handled everything and we just enjoyed the day."</li>
        <li><strong>Corporate event:</strong> "Our annual conference was flawless. The AV setup, catering coordination, and staff professionalism were exceptional."</li>
        <li><strong>Coordinator praise:</strong> "Our event coordinator was worth her weight in gold. Nothing slipped through the cracks."</li>
        <li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> "They worked with our outside vendors seamlessly and gave us the flexibility to make it truly ours."</li>
        <li><strong>Guests:</strong> "Guest after guest told us it was the best party they'd ever attended. That says it all."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your practice</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your homepage, service pages, and about page.</li>
        <li><strong>Send the collection link</strong> to happy clients right after a great result.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve each testimonial</strong> before it goes live — full control, always.</li>
        <li><strong>Watch it convert</strong> — visitors see real proof and take action.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Premium testimonials for premium bookings</h2>
      <p>Venues that command the highest rates have the strongest social proof. Testimonials from genuinely thrilled couples and event planners justify your pricing and attract the clientele who values what you offer. SocialProof gives you the tools to build and display that reputation on your website — free to start.</p>

      <div style="background:#f0fdf4;border-left:4px solid #16a34a;padding:1.5rem;margin:2.5rem 0;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 0.5rem;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
        <p style="margin:0;">No credit card. No contracts. Set up in under 5 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:3rem;">
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#16a34a;color:white;padding:1rem 2.5rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;">
          Start collecting testimonials free →
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
